reviewText: I purchased this for my granddaughter for her birthday.  She had seen both of the movies at my house on TV and she had never seen 102 Dalmatians movie at all.  She loved it and told me that is what I could get her for her birthday.  She loves it.
My son loved this movie set. and it was  much easier than looking for them one at a time Thanks
I love this DVD set. My kids love puppies and I have always loved these movies. It was great to be able to buy all of them in one package!
